{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember this incident, but my friend said she remembers that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had-- it was very scary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, Jewish children suddenly realized that people saw that even Jewish children weren't safe after the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was important to get out, to get the children out that did survive out as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we were chosen priority, six from this home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why, I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have a feeling maybe because I had a father and the others didn't have anybody, so they took priorities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They-- these were priority children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were various ages, from, I don't know, nine to-- I don't know exact ages.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was at that time-- it was in '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, this was the end of '45, so I must have been like-- 12 and 1/2. 12 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was 12 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there were various ages among the ones, the six-- under 10, 12, 13, 14, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because you can see on the-- if you look at the picture where I am with them, you can see we're each different-- different heights, and you can see that we are different ages.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's very clear to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so we six were chosen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was two sisters, a little boy who's very bright for his age, even smarter than I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I thought I was smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was brighter than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was so bright that we-- we thought he was genius.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was a genius.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was only maybe seven or eight at that time, under 10, and he was like a genius.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So you talk about smart children surviving, he was even smarter than any of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we thought he was brilliant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he-- we always laughed when he spoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
